Mysterify is a Google Chrome extension that adds a bit of fun to your web browsing by displaying an entrance video of Rey Mysterio on 1 out of every 10 page loads.

Key Features:

- Random Appearances: Each time you open a new web page, there is a 1/10 chance that an entrance video of Rey Mysterio will appear.
- Light Entertainment: Ideal for wrestling fans or anyone who enjoys a light-hearted surprise.
- Inspired by Cenafy: Similar to the Cenafy extension that features John Cena, Mysterify offers a comparable experience with Rey Mysterio.

How It Works:

After installation, Mysterify will automatically run in the background. It monitors page loads and randomly decides whether to display an image of Rey Mysterio. This happens roughly once every ten page loads.

Why Use Mysterify:

Entertainment: Adds a touch of fun to your browsing.
Safe: Does not collect personal data or interfere with your browsing.
Install Mysterify to bring a small, enjoyable surprise to your web browsing experience.
